Package org.apache.axis2.jaxws.dispatchers

Class Summary
GenericProviderDispatcher This dispatcher will look for a specific operation on the AxisService and return it if found.
MustUnderstandChecker Plugin to remove "understood" headers for the JAXWS related headers.
MustUnderstandUtils Static utility methods used in processing mustUnderstand headers relative to JAXWS.
MustUnderstandValidationDispatcher Do JAXWS MustUnderstand header processing per the JAXWS 2.0 specification.
